Bourne shell and Python scripts for GNU/Linux and Unix.

This project has been tested on the following platforms:

+===========+===============+===============================+
| OS Family | Distribution  | OS Version (OS Ports)         |
+===========+===============+===============================+
| GNU/Linux | Amazon Linux  | 2 (x86_64)                    |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux | CentOS        | 8 (x86_64)                    |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux | Debian        | 10 (amd64, s390x)             |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux | Fedora        | 32 (x86_64)                   |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux | openSUSE      | Leap 15.2 (x86_64)            |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux | openSUSE      | Tumbleweed 20200901 (x86_64)  |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux | Oracle Linux  | 8.2 (x86_64)                  |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux | Raspbian      | 10 (armhf)                    |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux | Red Hat       | Enterprise Linux 8.2 (x86_64) |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux | Ubuntu        | 18.04 LTS (amd64)             |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux | Ubuntu        | 19.10 (amd64)                 |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| Unix      | Apple macOS   | 10.15 (x86_64)                |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| Unix      | FreeBSD       | 11.3 (amd64)                  |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| Unix      | FreeBSD       | 12.1 (amd64)                  |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| Unix      | GhostBSD      | 20.04 (amd64)                 |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| Unix      | NetBSD        | 8.1 (amd64)                   |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| Unix      | NetBSD        | 8.2 (amd64)                   |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| Unix      | NetBSD        | 9.0 (amd64)                   |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+
| Unix      | OpenIndiana   | Hipster 2019.10 (x86_64)      |
+-----------+---------------+-------------------------------+

The various OS ports have been tested on the following processors:

+=========+====================================+=========+=========+
| CPU ISA | CPU Vendor and Microarchitecture   | 32 bit  | 64 bit  |
+---------+------------------------------------+---------+---------+
| ARMv8-A | ARM Cortex-A53                     | armhf   | aarch64 |
+---------+------------------------------------+---------+---------+
| x86-64  | Intel Silvermont, Kaby Lake,       | N/A     | amd64/  |
|         | and Coffee Lake                    |         | x86_64  |
+---------+------------------------------------+---------+---------+
| z/Arch  | IBM z900 via Hercules emulator     | N/A     | s390x   |
+---------+------------------------------------+---------+---------+
